{"tid":884524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"玉女修道8年變慾女　修女大解禁當AV女優","createTime":"2018-10-31T16:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T02:15:20.000Z","uid":72009,"like":44,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fa8034097ab4d59307705c7f93278be2d38b4399","tid":884524,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T16:04:41.000Z","msg":"據英國《太陽報》與《鏡報》報導，潘內達從10歲開始就進入修道院，原本要修練成為一名專業修女，但沒想到8年的修道，反而讓她從玉女變成慾女。潘內達說，在修道院的生活一切都算美好，但直到她愛上了一名宗教老師之後，內心的慾望大開，之後離開修道院，進入一般職場工作。就在她進入雀巢公司工作時，被星探布托斯(Juan Bustos)挖掘，一腳踏入成人影片界。<br />\n潘內達更說，平時的她最愛自慰和拍AV，但仍不忘自己的信仰，周日都會固定到教會做彌撒。潘內達也說，AV工作是「正派且藝術」，她覺得並沒有什麼不好。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181031/640_583f521d030ef4d6b70fcc350aa80c55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181031%2F640_583f521d030ef4d6b70fcc350aa80c55.jpg&h=9f7a14cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181031/640_d0fe5022f81de340aecc0de64b405731.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181031%2F640_d0fe5022f81de340aecc0de64b405731.jpg&h=2c6a2ab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181031/640_771c00a124be9050c6bbacbbdef6e48d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181031%2F640_771c00a124be9050c6bbacbbdef6e48d.jpg&h=32b19563&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30820117ca144a46c51c3465c24d704a2c371bca","tid":884524,"uid":77355,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T16:06:19.000Z","msg":"我有罪!快D用緊水淋我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1802b2537a442b41f714cfa57d28ff3b321b0a3","tid":884524,"uid":564